<hw>cosh</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a piece of leather-covered metal with a
flexible handle; used for hitting people.</def> <mark>[slang]</mark>
⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> blackjack, sap.</syn>⟦br⟧
